metadata.name: Contours in Black & White
metadata.description:
Genesis piece of High Contrast Black & White portraits I have taken recently.  
I want to share my experiments, my journey and my passion with others and thus making this available is both a Thank you to all the supporters I have had thus far and a welcome to those that see my work, appreciate it and if it resonates with you to welcome you to pick one up and join my journey.  
Photography is a medium where I get to connect on so many levels, with talented individuals globally.  
I want to continue to grow my network, connect and collect from others and while doing it learn more, explore and experiment more with the skills I have.
